snippet.title: 5 Children in Crystal City - Texas AMBER Alert (EAS #171)
snippet.description:
I thought we could go the whole month without AMBER Alerts, unfortunately, the answer was no. 

Text Product: https://mesonet.agron.iastate.edu/wx/afos/p.php?pil=CAECRP&e=202008142108

BULLETIN - EAS ACTIVATION REQUESTED
CHILD ABDUCTION EMERGENCY
TEXAS DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY
RELAYED BY NATIONAL WEATHER SERVICE CORPUS CHRISTI TX
408 PM CDT FRI AUG 14 2020

THE FOLLOWING MESSAGE IS TRANSMITTED AT THE REQUEST OF THE TEXAS
DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY.

THE ZAVALA COUNTY SHERIFFS OFFICE IS SEARCHING FOR JUSTINE KAYLEE
LOPEZ, WHITE, FEMALE, 10 YEARS OLD, 4 FEET 5 INCHES, 80 POUNDS, BLACK
HAIR, BLACK EYES. JOLYNE KAYLYNN LOPEZ, WHITE, FEMALE, 9 YEARS OLD, 4
FEET 3 INCHES, 60 POUNDS, BLACK HAIR, AND BLACK EYES. RUBEN LOPEZ JR,
WHITE, MALE, 7 YEARS OLD. JORDAN LOPEZ, WHITE, MALE, 4 YEARS OLD, 3
FEET 3 INCHES, 40 POUNDS, BLACK HAIR AND BLACK EYES. JAYDEN LEE
LOPEZ, WHITE, MALE, 11 MONTHS OLD.

VICTIMS WERE LAST SEEN AT 11:25 AM ON 08/10/2020, IN CRYSTAL 
CITY, TX. POLICE ARE LOOKING FOR RUBEN LOPEZ, WHITE, MALE, 29 
YEARS OLD, 5 FOOT 6 INCHES, 150 POUNDS, BLACK EYES AND BROWN HAIR 
IN CONNECTION WITH THIS ABDUCTION. POLICE ARE ALSO LOOKING FOR 
ROXANNE FUENTES, WHITE, FEMALE, 31 YEARS OLD, 5 FEET 8 INCHES, 120
POUNDS, BLACK EYES AND BROWN HAIR IN CONNECTION WITH THIS 
ABDUCTION.

THE SUSPECTS ARE DRIVING A GRAY, 2008, CHEVY, TRAIL BLAZER WITH A
TX, LICENSE PLATE NUMBER OF M K V 2 7 0 2.

LAW ENFORCEMENT OFFICIALS BELIEVE THESE CHILDREN TO BE IN GRAVE OR
IMMEDIATE DANGER. 

IF YOU HAVE ANY INFORMATION REGARDING THIS ABDUCTION, CALL THE ZAVALA
COUNTY SHERIFF\U2019S OFFICE AT 8 3 0 3 7 4 3 6 1 5.

NEWS MEDIA POINT OF CONTACT IS ZAVALA COUNTY SHERIFF'S OFFICE AT 
8 3 0 3 7 4 3 6

$$
Intro and Outro Music:
Local Forecast (Elevator) - Kevin MacLeod (Pitched down by 5%)
